OL,3,CTrump's Irish merger comment 'clearly
OL,4,Ca joke', says deputy First Minister
OL,6,FThe deputy First Minister has played
OL,7,Fdown the impact of President Donald
OL,8,FTrump's ferocious criticism of the
OL,9,FPrime Minister in the Oval Office on
OL,10,FSt Patrick's Day.
OL,12,FThe President is angry at the UK and
OL,13,FNATO's failure to support him in his
OL,14,Fwar with Iran.
OL,16,FHowever, Emma Little Pengelly, who had
OL,17,Fa scheduled meeting with him in the
OL,18,FWhite House said that Mr Trump's views
OL,19,Fwill be likely to "evolve" over time.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
