OL,3,CTrump's Irish merger comment 'clearly
OL,4,Ca joke', says deputy First Minister
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, in the Oval Office
OL,7,FTaoiseach Micheal Martin had to step
OL,8,Fin to defend Prime Minister Keir
OL,9,FStarmer from a barrage of criticism
OL,10,Ffrom the President, over what he sees
OL,11,Fas the UK and NATO's failure to
OL,12,Fsupport his war in the Middle East.
OL,14,FElsewhere on Wednesday,
OL,15,Frepresentatives from Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fand the Republic of Ireland were
OL,17,Fpresent at the British ambassador to
OL,18,Fthe US, Sir Christian Turner's, St
OL,19,FPatrick's Day breakfast.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
