OL,3,CTrump's Irish merger comment 'clearly
OL,4,Ca joke', says deputy First Minister
OL,6,FStormont Health Minister Mike Nesbitt,
OL,7,FSpeaker Edwin Poots, UUP leader Jon
OL,8,FBurrows and PSNI Chief Constable Jon
OL,9,FBoutcher were among those in
OL,10,Fattendance.
OL,12,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill,
OL,13,Fdeclined to go to the White House in
OL,14,Fprotest at the US policy on Gaza.
OL,16,FAlliance leader Naomi Long and SDLP
OL,17,Fleader Claire Hanna also stayed away.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
